    "This way, case studies can typologize and categorize interventions across events to identify process changes attributable to DSA mechanisms like notice-andtakedown procedures (Article 14), advertising transparency provisions (Article 24), or coordinated oversight under the European Board for Digital Services (Article 47), as performed by similar comparative case studies [86,152].",
    "Mixed methods researchStrategically combining quantitative and qualitative methods through careful integration and triangulation allows developing robust, multi-faceted understandings of the DSA's complex impacts.",
